!! dpm input file. Readed in input_data_dpm subroutine

!!!****DPM control parameters****!!!
.false.                                             ! use_dpm [true|false].                             Default: false
.false. 1.d0                                        ! dpm_subiter, dpm_dt_max:                          Turn on sub-iterations for particles, maximum time-step size for the dpm subiter
0                                                   ! setnump:                                          Set number of particles: 0 - by mass flow rate, 1 - by value
30.0d-3                                             ! dpm_mass_flow:                                    Mass flow rate of real particles 
1 9999                                             	! dpm_nparticles, dpm_inject:                       Number of computational particles to be injected at each step, number of time steps to inject particles
1                                                   ! nreal_part:                                       Number of real particles in one computacional particle 
2                                                   ! diamdp:                                           Diameter distribution: 0 - constant, 1 - normal, 2 - log_normal 
300.0d-6  50.0d-6                                   ! dpm_mean_diam, dpm_std_diam:                      Diameter distribution parameters [diameter mean, diameter standard deviation] *Choose values ​​in the same order of magnitude
745.042756924d0                                     ! dpm_rho:                                          Specific mass *Or define expression in dpm_evap
1.33065142465d-3                                    ! dpm_mu:                                           Dynamic viscosity 
1                                                   ! initposd:                                         Initial position distribution: 0 - coordinates, 1 - circular inlet, 2 - rectangular inlet, 3 - annular inlet 
0.0d0   0.032d0   0.032d0                           ! dpm_x0, dpm_y0, dpm_z0:                           Initial position by coordinates [x0, y0, z0]
0.0d0   0.0d0   0.0d0  1.0d0  0.0d0   1.0d0         ! inlet_(x1,x2,y1,y2,z1,z2):                        Circular/rectangular inlet plane [x1,x2] x [y1,y2] x [z1,z2] *Just planes parallel to xy, xz, yz ...
0.032d0   0.032d0   1.5d-3  0.0d0                   ! inlet_center_(1,2), inlet_length_(1,2):           Circular/rectangular inlet geometry: [center_pos1, center_pos2] / [diameter_ex/length_edge1, diameter_in/length_edge2]
.false.  0  0.0d0   0.0d0   0.0d0   0.0d0           ! dpm_initall, volume_type, volume_(1,2,3,r):       Initiate a volume of particles by value: .true. or .false / 0 - Cylinder [pos_1, pos_2], 1 - Sphere [xc, yc, zc, r], 2 - parallelepiped [center_posY, length_edgeY]
150.0d0   0.0d0   0.0d0                             ! dpm_(u0,v0,w0):                                   Initial mean velocities [u0, v0, w0]
0.0d0   5.0d0   5.0d0                               ! dpm_(u0_,v0_,w0_):                                Initial standard deviation velocities [u0_, v0_, w0_]
0.0d0   0.0d0   0.0d0                               ! dpm_omega_(x0,y0,z0):                             Initial angular velocities [omega_x0, omega_y0, omega_z0]
1   1   1   0  1                                    ! dpm_forces(1,2,3,4,5):                            Considered forces: 0 - Deactivate, 1 - Activate [Weigth, Buoyancy, Shear Lift Force, Rotational Lift Force, virtual mass] *Drag always considered
4                                                   ! dpm_coupling:                                     Coupling type: 1-way coupling, 2-way coupling, 4-way coupling (deterministic DPM model), 5-DEM and 6-Adaptative coupling type
0                                                   ! dpm_collision_type                                Collision type: 0 - noone, 1- stochastic, 2- deterministic

!!!****Domain Boundaries control parameters****!!
2   2   1   1   2   2                               ! dpm_boundary(1,2,3,4,5,6):                        Condition type for domain boundaries: 0 - Deletion, 1 - Reflection, 2 - Periodic, 3 - Free_slip at [WEST, EAST, SOUTH, NORTH, BOTTOM, TOP]
1.0d0                                               ! dpm_wall_restitution_coeff:                       Wall-particle coefficient of restitution
0.0d0                                               ! dpm_wall_friction_coeff:                          Wall-particle coefficient of dynamic friction
0  0.0d0                                            ! dpm_wall_roughness, std_roughness:                Roughness surface: 0 - no, 1 - yes / and standard deviation of roughness
0                                                   ! dpm_ib_use:                                       Wall-particle collision with a immersed geometry: 0 - no, 1 - yes
1                                                   ! dpm_imb_io:                                       Particle position related to the immersed geometry: outside = -1, inside = 1 

!!!****Inter-particle collision model control parameters - 4-way coupling****!!
